{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"0679f013195d54907b43cefc38239c86","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The 5 layers are there but the colors are inconsistent:\n- Astrologia: '#7C5CFF' (purple) — P2\n- Tântrica: '#2DD4BF' (teal) — P3\n- I-Ching: '#A0763A' (brown) — P5\n- Cabala: '#7C5CFF' (purple — SAME as Astrologia) — P1\n- Odus: '#F0B429' (gold) — P4\n\nTwo bugs:\n1. Cabala and Astrologia share the same color (#7C5CFF)\n2. Color order doesn't match Pilar numbers 1-5 consistently\n\nThis is a small surgical fix. F-203 is partly done but needs unique colors per Pilar.\n\nLet me pick a different, higher-impact task. Looking at the queue:\n- F-200: Integrate R-030 (akasha.calcular) with real engines @akasha/core-* — P0\n- F-203: MandalaChart 5 cores — P1 (mostly done, just color fix needed)\n- F-204: Replace stubs — P2\n- F-207: 3 test profiles — P1\n\nF-200 is P0 and the most impactful. Let me check the state of R-030 integration.","signature":"527010b46ff067abc6f973d533a24c72ef810c93714c9e4e14a81d620b8576ad"}],"model":"MiniMax-M3","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"service_tier":"standard"},"service_tier":"standard","context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"824bb878-318d-4e84-8c5b-e92c1bf98e2d","uuid":"0616e434-4f79-4aca-8743-98199cd61373"}
